refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
public voidYaf_Application::execute callableentry string...
This method is typically used to run Yaf_Application in a crontab work. Make the crontab work can also use the autoloader and Bootstrap mechanism.

  &reftitle.examples;

   Yaf_Application::executeexample


<?php
function main($argc, $argv) {
}

$config = array(
    "application" => array(
        "directory" => realpath(dirname(__FILE__)) . "/application",
    ),
);

/** Yaf_Application */
$application = new Yaf_Application($config);
$application->execute("main", $argc,  $argv);
?>


